  "instructions": [
    {
      "name": "initialize",
      "docs": [
        "One-time setup. Records the stake mint, the admin and the backend",
        "operator key, and the minimum stake (in raw token units, so it works",
        "with any mint decimals). Only the program's upgrade authority may call",
        "this — otherwise anyone could front-run the deploy and seize the",
        "singleton config forever."
      ],
