    {
      "name": "set_mint",
      "docs": [
        "Swap the accepted mint (admin only). Used to replace the devnet test",
        "token with the real $FRAD once it launches. Migration: providers fully",
        "unstake first (this closes their vault), then restake after the swap —",
        "the vault is re-created with the new mint. Providers who miss the",
        "window can still withdraw: `unstake` validates the mint against the",
        "vault, not the config."
      ],
