    {
      "name": "unstake",
      "docs": [
        "Withdraw staked $FRAD. Partial withdrawals must leave at least the",
        "minimum stake. Withdrawing everything deactivates the provider (the",
        "record and its signal history stay on-chain forever), sweeps the whole",
        "vault balance — including any tokens mistakenly sent to the vault",
        "directly — and closes the vault, so a later restake re-creates it with",
        "whatever mint is configured at that time."
      ],
